OL,3,CDemolition of derelict hotel gets
OL,4,Cunderway
OL,6,FA derelict hotel in Bristol is being
OL,7,Fknocked down.
OL,9,FThe demolition of the Grosvenor Hotel,
OL,10,Fopposite Temple Meads station, is
OL,11,Ffinally getting underway.
OL,13,FDemolition crews from TR Demolition
OL,14,Farrived on Thursday 1 February to
OL,15,Fbegin the task of carefully
OL,16,Fdismantling the hotel.
OL,18,FOn Saturday 3 February work stepped up
OL,19,Fwith a full demolition taking place.
