OL,3,CDemolition of derelict hotel gets
OL,4,Cunderway
OL,6,FThe hotel was badly-damaged by fire in
OL,7,FOctober 2022, leaving it unsafe and in
OL,8,Fneed of demolition.
OL,10,FThe pavement and part of the road at
OL,11,FTemple Way has been cordoned off since
OL,12,Fthen to form a wide enough exclusion
OL,13,Fzone around the building.
OL,15,FThe hotel has had a slow decline since
OL,16,Fits heyday before the Second World
OL,17,FWar, and in the 1950s and 60s, when it
OL,18,Fwas one of the landmark buildings for
OL,19,Fpeople arriving in Bristol via Temple
OL,20,FMeads station.
