OL,3,CDemolition of derelict hotel gets
OL,4,Cunderway
OL,6,FBy the 1990s it was being used as a
OL,7,Fhostel for homeless people, and that
OL,8,Fclosed down around 25 years ago.
OL,10,FIt is unclear what, if anything, will
OL,11,Fhappen to the site once the hotel has
OL,12,Fgone.
